2eb8779b1016ca5e489c9725bbe5d9e14837c1f5.name: FlixBus
2eb8779b1016ca5e489c9725bbe5d9e14837c1f5.conditionsSummary: Non-exchangeable. Non-exchangeable. Up to 100% of the ticket price refund in the form of a voucher: issued at 25% of the ticket price for cancellations less than 1 day before departure, 50% between 1 and 6 days, 75% between 7 and 29 days, and 100% for cancellations made 30 days or more in advance. Please visit https://www.flixbus.com/service/change-cancel-a-booking/cancellation-policy. Service fee included in the price and no refundable.
